Name: Pack Per Duck
About the game: Ugly duckling came up with a brilliant plan. Ugly duckling decided to Rob a Bank. I put on a bag and flew, but the bag flew off. He needs more packages to collect, so that his face could not be identified! Pack per Duck-2d shooter with a change of weapons, go through various levels dodging mines, enemy bullets and suicide bombers, destroy levels, blow up everything around and at the end meet the great and terrible... a rubber duck! Management: WASD-Movement Mouse wheel - change weapons Left Mouse Button-Shooting R-Recharge F-Throw a grenade Feature of game: - Complexity - Beautiful Pixel-Art - Music
